  "_comment": "Generic engine mechanic (see laser/combat.py hpt_clone_cfg / HPTClone) \u2014 any character's JSON can opt in via this same block. Each threshold fires ONCE EVER per crossing (non-repeatable), spawning a stationary 1-HP clone at each listed corner. Clones never move, are hittable by enemy ranged/petal contact (die on any single hit), and attack only via their own orbiting sphere.",
